{
  "stem": "9590.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "I was taken to work every day, near the city of Rivne.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "The Germans built an airport, and they took workers there to build it up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "Some people worked on the roads, because our town was on the main road that the German army went from Germany to Russia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "So their heavy equipment broke the roads, and they made sure that the roads are fixed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I worked on that airport probably for a month.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "So every day they picked us up and they brought us there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And we worked all day long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "And then in the evening, they brought us back home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "After a few weeks of working there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was injured.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And my-- all of a sudden I felt a rock hit my head.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "And I was bleeding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They took me into an infirmary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "There was a German infirmary there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had very long braids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "So in order for them to see the wound, because I was bleeding profusely, they unbraided the hair.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And the Germans said, [GERMAN], that I  have beautiful hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "The fact that my life was at stake, he didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "They couldn't do much because the wound was very deep.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "So they sent me to Rivne to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And there they stitched it up, and they bandaged the head, and they said that they think-- the doctors there said that they think that I'm out of danger.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I came back home, my mother was furious.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened to you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told her the story, as long as my life was not in danger.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they did not take me anymore to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stayed home.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
